{
  "$schema": "https://vega.github.io/schema/vega-lite/v5.json",
  "description": "This is a regression of the percentage of electricity generated from renewable energy on CO2 emissions per capita in the UK from 1985 - 2018. I chose to stop at 2018 because this was before Covid, which I feel might have influenced the results due to lower emissions in general. I performed the regression in python to determine the equaition of the regression line",
  "title": {
    "text": [
      "Regression of carbon intensity of electricity on CO2 ",
